      <p>The AI Brain is one of the most thoughtfully implemented parts of the platform. Two separate AI layers exist: <code>brain.ts</code> (TypeScript class, Anthropic SDK) and <code>ai-orchestrator.js</code> (axios-based, three specialist agents). Both are well-structured and serve different purposes.</p>

